quran[5{c,v,t}:
48,24,"wohi hai jis ne mecca ki waadi mein unn ke haath tum se aur tumahray haath unn se rok diye, halaank woh unn par tumhe ghalba ataa kar chuka tha aur jo kuch tum kar rahay thay Allah usay dekh raha tha"
48,25,"wohi log to hain jinhon ne kufar kya aur tum ko masjid haraam se roka aur Huda ke avnton ko unn ki qurbani ki jagah nah pounchanay diya agar ( mecca mein ) aisay momin mard o aurat mojood nah hotay jinhein tum nahi jantay, aur yeh khatrah nah hota ke nadanstgi mein tum inhen pamaal kar do ge aur is se tum par harf aeye ga ( to jung nah roki jati roki woh is liye gayi ) taakay Allah apni rehmat mein jis ko chahay daakhil kar le woh momin allag ho gay hotay to ( ahal mecca mein se ) jo kafir thay un ko hum zaroor sakht saza dete"
48,26,( yahi wajah hai ke ) jab un kafiroon ne apne dilon mein jahilana Hamiyat bitha li to Allah ne apne rasool aur mominoun par سکینت nazil farmai aur mominoun ko taqwa ki baat ka paband rakha ke wohi uss ke ziyada haq daar aur uss ke ahal thay Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai
48,27,"fi al waqea Allah ne apne rasool ko sacha khawab dikha ya tha jo theek theek haq ke mutabiq tha Insha Allah tum zaroor masjid haraam mein poooray aman ke sath daakhil ho ge, apne sir منڈواؤ ge aur baal ترشواؤ ge, aur tumhe koi khauf nah ho ga woh uss baat ko jaanta tha jisay tum nah jantay thay is liye woh khawab poora honay se pehlay uss ne yeh qareebi fatah tum ko ataa farma di"
48,28,woh Allah hi hai jis ne apne rasool ko hadaayat aur deen haq ke sath bheja hai taakay uss ko poori jins deen par ghalib kar day aur iss haqeeqat par Allah ki gawahi kaafi hai
